# admin-web

- Read **`admin-web/AGENTS.md`** before changing App Router, server components, or middleware. Next 16 may differ from older training data.
- Keep **admin API** and **Supabase admin** usage aligned with `admin-web/src/app/api/` and `admin-web/src/lib/` patterns.
- Use **Tailwind v4** conventions already present in the admin app; follow existing layout and dashboard structure.
